---
import { Check } from 'lucide-react';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="it">
    <head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
		<title>Applicazione Ricevuta | MONOCORE™</title>
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
    <body class="bg-void text-industrial antialiased selection:bg-brand-orange selection:text-void">
        
        <!-- Centered Content Container -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-6">
            <div class="max-w-2xl text-center">
                
                <!-- Success Icon (Neon Green) -->
                <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
                    <svg 
                        width="80" 
                        height="80" 
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24" 
                        fill="none" 
                        stroke="#00ff00" 
                        stroke-width="2" 
                        stroke-linecap="round" 
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        class="animate-pulse"
                    >
                        <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                </div>

                <!-- Headline -->
                <h1 class="font-sans font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-industrial uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">
                    APPLICAZIONE REGISTRATA
                </h1>

                <!-- Subheadline -->
                <p class="font-mono text-lg text-industrial/80 mb-12">
                    Il sistema ha processato la tua richiesta.
                </p>

                <!-- Body Copy (Instructions) -->
                <div class="font-mono text-sm md:text-base text-industrial/70 leading-relaxed mb-12">
                    <strong class="text-white">Cosa succede ora:</strong><br><br>
                    Ti ricontattiamo entro 24 ore via email o telefono per schedulare la Diagnostic Call.<br>
                    Nel frattempo, abbiamo inviato una conferma alla tua casella di posta. Se non la vedi, controlla la cartella spam.<br><br>
                    La Diagnostic Call dura 30-45 minuti e serve a verificare che il tuo processo di vendita sia compatibile con Monocore Revenue Path™.<br>
                    Non devi preparare nulla. Solo essere disponibile per la chiamata.
                </div>

                <!-- Primary CTA (Ghost Button) -->
                <a 
                    href="/" 
                    class="inline-block px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white text-white font-sans font-bold text-base uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-white hover:text-void transition-all duration-300 rounded-sm"
                >
                    TORNA ALLA HOME
                </a>

                <!-- Secondary Link -->
                <div class="mt-8">
                    <a 
                        href="/logs" 
                        class="font-mono text-sm text-industrial/50 hover:text-brand-orange hover:underline underline-offset-4 transition-colors"
                    >
                        Leggi il blog →
                    </a>
                </div>

                <!-- Support Micro-copy -->
                <p class="font-mono text-xs text-white/40 mt-16">
                    Hai domande? Rispondi all'email di conferma.
                </p>

            </div>
        </div>

    </body>
</html>
